data.description: Welcome home to 54 Clearblue Loop, right here in Nexton's prestigious Midtown community. This home is elegance and easy living all in one! It has an abundance of features starting with four bedrooms, a formal dining area, an office, a morning room, a stunning gourmet kitchen, and a third-floor loft that can easily be made into a 5th bedroom. Best of all, you'll love the massive corner lot where you can enjoy the view from double coastal porches that overlook a pond!Upon entering the home, you're instantly greeted by a bright hallway and gleaming floors that lead to a large private office space, complete with french doors. The formal dining room across the hall makes for the perfect setting to dine or use as additional living space. You'll pass the beautiful half bathroom before entering into the heart of the home, the kitchen! This kitchen is a gourmet chef's dream, it could easily be right out of a Charleston magazine! Sleek design surrounds you from floor to ceiling with upgraded cabinetry, a farm house sink, pot filler, upgraded hardware, stylish backsplash, quartz countertops, and so much more. The floor plan opens up from the kitchen to an eat-in dining space and a large living room. Tucked away in a private corner, is a light and bright morning room, a perfect spot for a coffee break, or to take a good book during some quiet time. The home also features custom shades throughout providing a true coastal feel.   Upstairs on the second floor you'll find all four bedrooms. The master suite is spacious with a walk-in closet, an upgraded walk-in shower, and quartz countertops. Upgraded hardware throughout the home brings a touch of elegance to an already beautiful space. Down the hall, you'll also find a secondary full bathroom and laundry room. The third floor features a large loft space complete with a closet that could easily be made into a bedroom. This is the perfect teen hang out, movie room, or office location, the options are endless!   This large, nearly quarter acre corner lot here in Nexton, invites you to imagine the endless options to make this this home into your own oasis! Across the street offers more privacy as it faces an adorable pond. Being so close to the entrance of Midtown also makes it easier to enjoy the amenities of the neighborhood or even a short golf cart ride away to Brighton Park Village's amenities. Just minutes from Downtown Nexton, featuring a wave of in-progress development with grocery stores, Nexton shops, and even the I-26 is close by. You truly are in the heart of it all! Come experience all that the Nexton community has to offer!
